ivardefs.name: approvalDate
ivardefs.desc: The date on which the asset content was approved by the publisher. Approval happens once when the content is officially approved for usage.

ivardefs.name: canFilterBy_
ivardefs.desc: List of properties by which Subscriptions on the topic can be filtered.

ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details to assist a user in finding and communicating with the publisher.

ivardefs.name: copyright
ivardefs.desc: A copyright statement relating to the Topic and/or its contents. Copyright statements are generally legal restrictions on the use and publishing of the Topic.

ivardefs.name: date
ivardefs.desc: For draft definitions, indicates the date of initial creation.  For active definitions, represents the date of activation.  For withdrawn definitions, indicates the date of withdrawal.

ivardefs.name: derivedFromCanonical_
ivardefs.desc: The canonical URL pointing to another FHIR-defined Topic that is adhered to in whole or in part by this Topic.

ivardefs.name: derivedFromUri_
ivardefs.desc: The URL pointing to an externally-defined subscription topic or other definition that is adhered to in whole or in part by this definition.

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A free text natural language description of the Topic from the consumer's perspective.

ivardefs.name: effectivePeriod
ivardefs.desc: The period during which the Topic content was or is planned to be effective.

ivardefs.name: experimental
ivardefs.desc: A flag to indicate that this Topic is authored for testing purposes (or education/evaluation/marketing), and is not intended to be used for genuine usage.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Business identifiers assigned to this Topic by the performer and/or other systems.  These identifiers remain constant as the resource is updated and propagates from server to server.

ivardefs.name: jurisdiction_
ivardefs.desc: A jurisdiction in which the Topic is intended to be used.

ivardefs.name: lastReviewDate
ivardefs.desc: The date on which the asset content was last reviewed. Review happens periodically after that, but doesn't change the original approval date.

ivardefs.name: publisher
ivardefs.desc: Helps establish the "authority/credibility" of the Topic.  May also allow for contact.

ivardefs.name: purpose
ivardefs.desc: Explains why this Topic is needed and why it has been designed as it has.

ivardefs.name: resourceTrigger
ivardefs.desc: The criteria for including updates to a nominated resource in the topic.  Thie criteria may be just a human readable description and/or a full FHIR search string or FHIRPath expression.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The current state of the Topic.

ivardefs.name: title
ivardefs.desc: A short, descriptive, user-friendly title for the Topic, for example, "admission".

ivardefs.name: url
ivardefs.desc: An absolute URL that is used to identify this Topic when it is referenced in a specification, model, design or an instance. This SHALL be a URL, SHOULD be globally unique, and SHOULD be an address at which this Topic is (or will be) published. The URL SHO

ivardefs.name: useContext_
ivardefs.desc: The content was developed with a focus and intent of supporting the contexts that are listed. These terms may be used to assist with indexing and searching of code system definitions.

ivardefs.name: version
ivardefs.desc: The identifier that is used to identify this version of the Topic when it is referenced in a specification, model, design or instance. This is an arbitrary value managed by the Topic author and is not expected to be globally unique. For example, it might

properties.desc: Describes a stream of resource state changes identified by trigger criteria and annotated with labels useful to filter projections from this topic.
